body:
@suharshs Thanks for the reply. The script that uses hub doesn't have `--architecture` flag.
As you've mentioned the retraining script, I think there's an issue with that script. Could you look into this?
https://github.com/googlecodelabs/tensorflow-for-poets-2/issues/64
The predictions when using hub script are erroneous.
